I"<p>We have published a Special issue on <a href="http://www.mdpi.com/journal/sensors/special_issues/indoor_sensors">Sensors for Indoor Mapping and Navigation</a>.</p>

<p>53 papers give an overview on the state-of-the art in indoor localisation, tracking and mapping.</p>

<p>Read about the papers in the <a href="http://www.mdpi.com/1424-8220/16/5/655">editorial</a>.</p>

